text=(:notitle:)%0a(:table valign=top:)%0a(:cellnr colspan=3 width=380 bgcolor=#74483f align=center:)%0a!!%25white%25Carl Bennison, -The Captain-%25white%25%0a(:cellnr rowspan=30 width=400 align=center:) http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ATFacQBssJg/UMK7k0Xli8I/AAAAAAAAAJ0/g1UliO9iIRU/s320/534347-rick_grimes_04.jpg%0a(:cellnr width=340 colspan=2 align=center:)%0ahttp://wantonwicked.gamingsandbox.com/wiki/images/wtf/headers/wtf_s.png%0a(:cellnr width=150 align=left:)'''Age:'''%0a(:cell width=190:) 35%0a(:cellnr width=150 align=left:)'''Height:'''%0a(:cell width=190:) 5'9"%0a(:cellnr width=150 align=left:)'''Build:'''%0a(:cell width=190:) Lean%0a(:cellnr width=150 align=left:)'''Profession:''' %0a(:cell width=190:) Captain of the Highway Patrol%0a(:cellnr width=150 align=left:)'''Public Effects:'''%0a(:cell width=190:) Wolf-blooded 2\\%0a%0a%0a(:cellnr width=150 align=left:)'''Player:''' %0a(:cell width=190:) NPC: LeeK%0a(:cellnr width=150 align=left:)'''Theme Music:''' %0a(:cell width=190:) [[http://www.youtube.com/ |Music]]%0a(:tableend:)%0a%25%25http://wantonwicked.gamingsandbox.com/wiki/images/wtf/headers/wtf_d.png%0aIf not in uniform, Captain Bennison prefers to dress in plain buttoned shirts and jeans with leather cowboy boots. He likes old country music and is very fond of spending time with his family when his hectic work schedule allows. He has two sons, a teenaged daughter, and a mortal wife. His daughter carries the Wolf-Blood and he secretly worries that she may undergo the First Change.%0a%0a[[%3c%3c]]%0a%25%25http://wantonwicked.gamingsandbox.com/wiki/images/wtf/headers/wtf_h.png%0aThere are few Wolf-Blooded who take as hard a line with the werewolves as Captain Bennison. In his county even the werewolves are expected to follow the rules of the law. Yet it's been a difficult fight trying to get all of the packs to see things in that light. There are some activities that are overlooked by this pillar of the community to keep the fragile peace and keep humanity out of the crossfire of werewolf conflict.%0a%0aCarl Bennison however is a lawman to his core. He tolerates some of the illegal activities of local pack members because he has little choice, but keeps an open line of communication between himself, his Wolf-Blooded family members, and the leaders of the different packs. His friendship with the leader of the Lords of Mourning Glory has kept most of the packs in line and it has afforded him a grudging amount of respect among his inhuman relations.%0a%0aHe is assigned to highway patrol.%0a%0a[[%3c%3c]]%0a%25%25http://wantonwicked.gamingsandbox.com/wiki/images/wtf/headers/wtf_rph.png%0a''Law Enforcement -'' Wolf-Blooded or werewolves looking to gain connections or a job working for the Savannah PD may come first to Captain Bennison. His family has a long line of service in the police department, particularly in the city's K-9 unit.%0a%0a''Crime Log -'' If something strange is going on in the city, chances are the police know something about it. This can be anything from disappearances, kidnappings, and killings to the more benign such as car thefts and traffic violations.%0a%0a''Family Man -'' Captain Bennison may request Player Characters to look after his family if he's received death threats from criminals or has reason to worry that his family will be targeted.%0a%0a[[%3c%3c]]%0a%25%25http://wantonwicked.gamingsandbox.com/wiki/images/wtf/headers/wtf_q.png%0a"I don't know how they did it in your town, but this ain't your town." %0a%0a%0a"..." - Name%0a%0a[[%3c%3c]]%0a%0a(:include CityBook.WerewolfNavigationBar:)
